      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant attention from its next owner. The engine currently runs roughly and may need a major overhaul, and the transmission is showing signs of slipping. Cosmetically, there is noticeable rust on the rocker panels, several large dents, and the interior upholstery is heavily worn with some tearing. It is recommended for someone looking for a major restoration project or a source for parts.",
